reviewText: This movie was pretty funny! The actors seemed a little inexperienced, but this wasn't too distracting. The production and soundtrack in some ways held the movie together, but the plot was fun and the humor pretty strong, and so, overall, this movie was better than average. I'd give it three and a half stars, mostly on the strength of the wacky humor.
